# IntelliForge AI OS — Landing Page
# Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript strict mode
- Tailwind CSS with custom IF design tokens (tailwind.config.ts)
- lucide-react for icons
- JetBrains Mono for code traces, Inter for UI

## Design Tokens (from tailwind.config.ts)
- `if-dark`    #0f172a  — page background
- `if-indigo`  #4f46e5  — primary brand
- `if-purple`  #7c3aed  — secondary
- `if-cyan`    #06b6d4  — accent / India layer
- `if-green`   #10b981  — success / eval layer
- `if-orange`  #f97316  — India layer
- `if-text`    #e2e8f0  — body text
- `if-text-dim` #94a3b8 — muted text
- `if-border`  #1e3a5f  — borders

## CSS Classes (globals.css)
- `.text-gradient-if`  — indigo→purple→cyan gradient text
- `.glass-card`        — frosted glass card
- `.glass-card-indigo` — indigo-tinted glass
- `.glass-card-cyan`   — cyan-tinted glass
- `.btn-primary`       — indigo gradient CTA button
- `.btn-secondary`     — ghost button
- `.tag-pill`          — small pill label (use with .tag-indigo etc)
- `.eyebrow`           — uppercase section label
- `.code-trace`        — JetBrains Mono code trace text
- `.harness-layer`     — left-bordered layer row

## Components
- `Navbar`       — fixed top nav with scroll detection
- `Hero`         — animated harness layer stack + code traces
- `Architecture` — 5-layer stack + 8-package SDK table
- `Products`     — IF portfolio as ForgeOS Cloud tenants
- `Roadmap`      — 5 build phases with timeline
- `Pricing`      — 4 tiers in INR (Free / ₹2,999 / ₹9,999 / Enterprise)
- `Waitlist`     — email capture with role selector
- `Footer`       — links + brand

